---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About - JESTFLY">
  <div class="container py-16 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About JESTFLY</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6">
      <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground">
        JESTFLY is a comprehensive platform designed to empower music artists, content creators, and their fans.
      </p>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe in creating a unified ecosystem where artists can showcase their talent,
          connect with their audience, and build sustainable careers in the music industry.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">What We Offer</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li><strong>Community Features:</strong> Connect with fellow artists and fans through posts, comments, and interactions</li>
          <li><strong>Demo Submission System:</strong> Submit your music and receive professional feedback</li>
          <li><strong>JestCoin Ecosystem:</strong> Our digital currency for seamless transactions and rewards</li>
          <li><strong>NFT Marketplace:</strong> Buy, sell, and collect unique digital art and music</li>
          <li><strong>Career Planning Tools:</strong> Visual canvas for planning your music career journey</li>
          <li><strong>Store:</strong> Purchase music, merchandise, and digital products</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Built for Performance</h2>
        <p>
          JESTFLY is built with cutting-edge technology including Astro for lightning-fast performance,
          React for interactive features, and Supabase for secure data management.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
